The presentation concept is defined for the statement but no fact values are defined in the instance document that use this line item in the table ele:StatementOfComprehensiveIncomeTable. In this case the concept ComprehensiveIncomeAttributableToOwnersOfParent is missing from the definition linkbase table nd should be added.
